                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-357-off1831 t18310908-357-cd1832"></join>, 1 beer-machine, value 16l.; 3 tables, value 3l.; 1 stove, value 5l.; 8 chairs, value 1l.; 2 fenders, value 10s.; 5 jugs, value 3s.; 1 saucepan, value 2s.; 4 brushes, value 1s.; 2 spitoons, value 1s.; 2 buckets, value 4s.; 4 yards of oil-cloth, value 4s.; 10 china plates, value 2s.; 5 dishes, value 5d., and 1 set of fire-irons, value 2s.
